metadata.name: TGW : Monday
metadata.description:
Everything is rapidly moving toward the "right" answer.

I am a visual stimulus addict.
There is no rational reason for this.

How irrational things can be done with the extremely rational tool of a computer?

A momentary stimulus before it becomes a word.

I want reflection, not agreement or understanding. These works may be completed when your unconscious reflects on them.

A few seconds of eternity in an age where everything happens too fast.
